{"id":413,"ayahs":[{"number":20,"arabic":"أَلَمْ تَرَوْا۟ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ سَخَّرَ لَكُم مَّا فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَمَا فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ وَأَسْبَغَ عَلَيْكُمْ نِعَمَهُۥ ظَٰهِرَةًۭ وَبَاطِنَةًۭ ۗ وَمِنَ ٱلنَّاسِ مَن يُجَٰدِلُ فِى ٱللَّهِ بِغَيْرِ عِلْمٍۢ وَلَا هُدًۭى وَلَا كِتَٰبٍۢ مُّنِيرٍۢ","translation":"ARE YOU NOT aware that God has made subservient to you all that is in the heavens and all that is on earth, and has lavished upon you His blessings, both outward and inward? And yet, among men there is many a one that argues about God without having any knowledge [of Him], without any guidance, and without any light-giving revelation;","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3489.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":23118,"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"কি না","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23119,"position":2,"arabic":"تَرَوْا۟","translation":"তোমরা দেখো","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23120,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23121,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23122,"position":5,"arabic":"سَخَّرَ","translation":"অধীন করে দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23123,"position":6,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23124,"position":7,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23125,"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23126,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশমন্ডলীর","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23127,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"ও যা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23128,"position":11,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23129,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23130,"position":13,"arabic":"وَأَسْبَغَ","translation":"এবং সম্পূর্ণ করে দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23131,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23132,"position":15,"arabic":"نِعَمَهُۥ","translation":"অনুগ্রহসমূহ তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23133,"position":16,"arabic":"ظَـٰهِرَةًۭ","translation":"প্রকাশ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23134,"position":17,"arabic":"وَبَاطِنَةًۭ ۗ","translation":"ও অপ্রকাশ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23136,"position":18,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","translation":"এবং মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23137,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23138,"position":20,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"কেউ কেউ (এমনও আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23139,"position":21,"arabic":"يُجَـٰدِلُ","translation":"তর্ক করে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23140,"position":22,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23141,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23142,"position":24,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23143,"position":25,"arabic":"عِلْمٍۢ","translation":"কোনো জ্ঞান","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23144,"position":26,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23145,"position":27,"arabic":"هُدًۭى","translation":"কোনো পথনির্দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23146,"position":28,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23147,"position":29,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبٍۢ","translation":"কোনো কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23148,"position":30,"arabic":"مُّنِيرٍۢ","translation":"দীপ্তিময়","audioUrl":"wbw/031_020_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23149,"position":31,"arabic":"٢٠","translation":"(২০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":21,"arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱتَّبِعُوا۟ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ قَالُوا۟ بَلْ نَتَّبِعُ مَا وَجَدْنَا عَلَيْهِ ءَابَآءَنَآ ۚ أَوَلَوْ كَانَ ٱلشَّيْطَٰنُ يَدْعُوهُمْ إِلَىٰ عَذَابِ ٱلسَّعِيرِ","translation":"and when such [people] are told to follow that which God has bestowed from on high, they answer, “Nay, we shall follow that which we found our forefathers believing in and doing!” Why - [would you follow your forefathers] even if Satan had invited them unto the suffering of the blazing flame?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3490.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":24145,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24146,"position":2,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24147,"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمُ","translation":"তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24148,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱتَّبِعُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা অনুসরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24149,"position":5,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24150,"position":6,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন\"","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24151,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24152,"position":8,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24153,"position":9,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"\"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24154,"position":10,"arabic":"نَتَّبِعُ","translation":"আমরা অনুসরণ করবো","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24155,"position":11,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24156,"position":12,"arabic":"وَجَدْنَا","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24157,"position":13,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24158,"position":14,"arabic":"ءَابَآءَنَآ ۚ","translation":"আমার পিতৃ-পুরুষদেরকে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24160,"position":15,"arabic":"أَوَلَوْ","translation":"কি যদিও","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24161,"position":16,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24162,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنُ","translation":"শয়তান (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24163,"position":18,"arabic":"يَدْعُوهُمْ","translation":"ডেকে আসছে তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24164,"position":19,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24165,"position":20,"arabic":"عَذَابِ","translation":"শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24166,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلسَّعِيرِ","translation":"জ্বলন্ত আগুনের (তবুও অনুসরণ করবেই)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_021_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24167,"position":22,"arabic":"٢١","translation":"(২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":22,"arabic":"۞ وَمَن يُسْلِمْ وَجْهَهُۥٓ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ وَهُوَ مُحْسِنٌۭ فَقَدِ ٱسْتَمْسَكَ بِٱلْعُرْوَةِ ٱلْوُثْقَىٰ ۗ وَإِلَى ٱللَّهِ عَٰقِبَةُ ٱلْأُمُورِ","translation":"Now whoever surrenders his whole being unto God, and is a doer of good withal, has indeed taken hold of a support most unfailing: for with God rests the final outcome of all events.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3491.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":25139,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25140,"position":2,"arabic":"يُسْلِمْ","translation":"সমর্পণ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25141,"position":3,"arabic":"وَجْهَهُۥٓ","translation":"চেহারাকে (নিজেকে) তার","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25142,"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَى","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25143,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25144,"position":6,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এমতাবস্হায় যে সে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25145,"position":7,"arabic":"مُحْسِنٌۭ","translation":"সৎকর্মপরায়ণ","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25146,"position":8,"arabic":"فَقَدِ","translation":"তবে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25147,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱسْتَمْسَكَ","translation":"সে শক্ত করে ধরেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25148,"position":10,"arabic":"بِٱلْعُرْوَةِ","translation":"নিয়ে হাতলকে (অর্থাৎ আশ্রয়কে)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25149,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْوُثْقَىٰ ۗ","translation":"সুদৃঢ়","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25151,"position":12,"arabic":"وَإِلَى","translation":"এবং দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25152,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌রই","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25153,"position":14,"arabic":"عَـٰقِبَةُ","translation":"পরিণাম","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25154,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلْأُمُورِ","translation":"সব ব্যাপারের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_022_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25155,"position":16,"arabic":"٢٢","translation":"(২২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":23,"arabic":"وَمَن كَفَرَ فَلَا يَحْزُنكَ كُفْرُهُۥٓ ۚ إِلَيْنَا مَرْجِعُهُمْ فَنُنَبِّئُهُم بِمَا عَمِلُوٓا۟ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ عَلِيمٌۢ بِذَاتِ ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"But as for him who is bent on denying the truth - let not his denial grieve thee: unto Us they must return, and then We shall make them [truly] understand all that they were doing [in life]: for, verily, God has full knowledge of what is in the hearts [of men].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3492.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":26246,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26247,"position":2,"arabic":"كَفَرَ","translation":"অবিশ্বাস করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26248,"position":3,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"অতঃপর না (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26249,"position":4,"arabic":"يَحْزُنكَ","translation":"চিন্তিত করে তোমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26250,"position":5,"arabic":"كُفْرُهُۥٓ ۚ","translation":"অবিশ্বাস তার","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26252,"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَيْنَا","translation":"দিকে আমাদেরই","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26253,"position":7,"arabic":"مَرْجِعُهُمْ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্তন তাদের ( হবে )","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26254,"position":8,"arabic":"فَنُنَبِّئُهُم","translation":"তখন আমরা জানিয়ে দিবো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26255,"position":9,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26256,"position":10,"arabic":"عَمِلُوٓا۟ ۚ","translation":"তারা করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26258,"position":11,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26259,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26260,"position":13,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۢ","translation":"খুব অবহিত","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26261,"position":14,"arabic":"بِذَاتِ","translation":"সম্পর্কে অবস্থা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26262,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"অন্তরসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_023_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26263,"position":16,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"نُمَتِّعُهُمْ قَلِيلًۭا ثُمَّ نَضْطَرُّهُمْ إِلَىٰ عَذَابٍ غَلِيظٍۢ","translation":"We will let them enjoy them­selves for a short while - but in the end We shall drive them into suffering severe.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3493.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":27302,"position":1,"arabic":"نُمَتِّعُهُمْ","translation":"আমরা ভোগ করতে দিবো তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27303,"position":2,"arabic":"قَلِيلًۭا","translation":"অল্প (কাল)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27304,"position":3,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27305,"position":4,"arabic":"نَضْطَرُّهُمْ","translation":"আমরা বাধ্য করবো তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27306,"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27307,"position":6,"arabic":"عَذَابٍ","translation":"শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27308,"position":7,"arabic":"غَلِيظٍۢ","translation":"কঠিন","audioUrl":"wbw/031_024_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27309,"position":8,"arabic":"٢٤","translation":"(২৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":25,"arabic":"وَلَئِن سَأَلْتَهُم مَّنْ خَلَقَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ لَيَقُولُنَّ ٱللَّهُ ۚ قُلِ ٱلْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ ۚ بَلْ أَكْثَرُهُمْ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"AND THUS it is [with most people]: if thou ask them, “Who is it that has created the heavens and the earth?” - they will surely answer, “God.” Say: “[Then you ought to know that] all praise is due to God!”- for most of them do not know [what this implies].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3494.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":28347,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَئِن","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28348,"position":2,"arabic":"سَأَلْتَهُم","translation":"তুমি প্রশ্ন করো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28349,"position":3,"arabic":"مَّنْ","translation":"\"কে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28350,"position":4,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","translation":"সৃষ্টি করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28351,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশ মন্ডলী","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28352,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"ও পৃথিবী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28353,"position":7,"arabic":"لَيَقُولُنَّ","translation":"অবশ্যই তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28354,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","translation":"\"আল্লাহ্‌\"","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28356,"position":9,"arabic":"قُلِ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28357,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْحَمْدُ","translation":"\"সব প্রশংসা","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28358,"position":11,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ ۚ","translation":"জন্যে আল্লাহ্‌রই\"","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28360,"position":12,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28361,"position":13,"arabic":"أَكْثَرُهُمْ","translation":"অধিকাংশ (লোক) তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28362,"position":14,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28363,"position":15,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"তারা জানে","audioUrl":"wbw/031_025_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28364,"position":16,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ مَا فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ هُوَ ٱلْغَنِىُّ ٱلْحَمِيدُ","translation":"Unto God belongs all that is in the heavens and on earth. Verily, God alone is self-sufficient, the One to whom all praise is due!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3495.mp3","surahId":31,"words":[{"id":29252,"position":1,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ","translation":"জন্যে আল্লাহ্‌রই","audioUrl":"wbw/031_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29253,"position":2,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/031_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29254,"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/031_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29255,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশমন্ডলীর","audioUrl":"wbw/031_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29256,"